<br>
malosini/Mala etc generate almost NO aggro, you can be taunted off by almost anything <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START ;) --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/wink.gif ALT=";)"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END-->  Only problem I have as main debuffer on raids is that I cast it STRAIGHT AWAY on mobs, so am very high on hate list and ten to get smashed because I was *first* on hate list.<br>
Othwerwise I almost never get aggro from those spells.<br>
<br>
malosini is -60 to ALL resists bar disease. it makes a huge difference.<br>
Was in the Chef in Seb, low lvl vhanter 53/54? very very poor control and she was always having resist problems, don't think she had Charisma gear on /boggle. Rather than nuke I just started malosini every krup. mezz lands easy then, but she STILL tashed...needless ot say, she got ate several times<br>
*rolls eyes*.<br>
<br>
oh and casting in melee ranges reduces resists, and I dont care what others say that's my experience over the years debuffing/nuking on raids/xp. So PB AOE = less resists anyway.<br>
<br>
Redorious<br>
